t was found that [[GK Films]] plans to produce a horror film inspired by the song, directed by [[Kenny Ortega]] and produced with [[Ivan Reitman]].<ref>{{cite web|last1=Fleming Jr.|first1=Mike|title=Michael Jackson Song 'Thriller' In Center Of Pic Auction|url=https://deadline.com/2010/10/michael-jackson-song-thriller-in-center-of-pic-auction-79039/|website=Deadline|accessdate=16 January 2017}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.digitaltrends.com/movies/michael-jacksons-thriller-to-become-a-film-soon/|title=Michael Jackson's Thriller to become a feature-length movie|date=2010-10-29|newspaper=Digital Trends|access-date=2017-02-06|language=en-US}}</ref> As of February 2016, there has been no further news.\n\n==See also==\n* [[List of best-selling singles]]\n* [[List of best-selling singles in the United States]]\n* [[List of most expensive music videos]]\n* \"[[Michael Jackson's Thriller (music video)|Michael Jackson's Thriller]]\"\n* [[Thriller (viral video)]]\n* [[Thrill the World]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n;Bibliography\n{{Refbegin}}\n* {{cite book|last=Brooks|first=Darren|title=Michael Jackson: An Exceptional Journey|publisher=Chrome Dreams|year=2002|isbn=1-84240-178-5}}\n* [[Nelson George|George, Nelson]] (2004). ''[[Michael Jackson: The Ultimate Collection]]'' booklet. [[Sony BMG]].\n* {{cite book|last=Grant|first=Adrian|title=Michael Jackson: The Visual Documentary|publisher=Omnibus Press|year=2009|isbn=978-1-84938-261-8}}\n* {{cite book|last=Jones|first=Jel |title=Michael Jackson, the King of Pop: The Big Picture: the Music! the Man! the Legend! the Interviews! |year = 2005 |publisher=Amber Books Publishing|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=LuEPnk7irOMC&lpg=PP1&dq=Michael%20Jackson%2C%20the%20King%20of%20Pop%3A%20The%20Big%20Picture%3A&pg=PP1#v=onepage&q&f=true|isbn=0-9749779-0-X}}\n* {{cite book|last=Taraborrelli|first=J. Randy|authorlink=J. Randy Taraborrelli|title=The Magic and the Madness|year=2004|publisher=Headline|location=Terra Alta,